  scenario="It is Sunday afternoon. A business park manager messages: 'Afternoon — I manage a serviced office complex in Didcot with sixty car parking spaces across two buildings. Three of our tenants have asked about EV charging this month and one has said they will not renew their lease unless we install chargers. I would like eight 7kW chargers initially — four on each building wall — with the option to double that. We need payment capability because multiple companies share the car park, and we want usage reports per tenant. The buildings have three-phase supplies. What charger brands do you recommend for a multi-tenant setup? Can you survey both buildings next week? Budget is approved.' Without AI Messenger, the serviced office complex waits until Monday. With AI Messenger, the reply confirms your workplace and OCPP expertise, asks about the cable run distance from each building's distribution board to the proposed charger positions and whether existing cable containment exists, and captures: Didcot serviced office 60 spaces 2 buildings, 3 tenants requesting 1 threatening lease, 8×7kW initial doubling option, payment multi-tenant, usage reports per tenant, three-phase, brand recommendation, survey 2 buildings next week, budget approved."
